that meddlesome Rohan at bay.

6
00:00:13,490 --> 00:00:16,390
I dare say you’re a chip
right off the old block.

7
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:19,630
Shinobu: Like I said, you’ve got
the wrong number. Goodbye.

8
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:21,800
- Kira: I’m proud of you, boy.
- Shinobu: Happens all the time.

9
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:23,700
Kira: Now I have
even more reason

10
