But, first,
the adults need to talk.

12
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:29,670
( Hayato shudders )

13
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:31,410
Kira: Honeybunch,

14
00:00:31,470 --> 00:00:33,510
i’d love a goodbye kiss
before I leave.

15
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:34,580
Shinobu: Huh?

16
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:37,450
- ( Sighs )
- ( Kira chuckles )

17
00:00:38,510 --> 00:00:40,620
( Hayato gasping )

18
00:00:44,550 --> 00:00:45,790
- ( Porcelain shatters )
- ( Both gasp )

19
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:47,790
( Shinobu shrieks )

20
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:49,660
What are you doing, hayato?!

21
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,330
That’s my expensive China!

22
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:54,530
Why would you do that?
What’s wrong with you?!

23
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:57,470
I never know what’s going on
inside that head of yours!

24
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,470
You act like you don’t hear me,
and I don’t know why!

25
00:01:00,540 --> 00:01:03,070
- ( Hayato gasps )
- Shinobu: Where did I go wrong?

26
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:04,070
( Sobs )

27
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:05,510
♪

28
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:11,680
Hayato: You can’t
see it yet, mom,

29
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:13,750
but he’s a murderous psycho.

30
00:01:13,820 --> 00:01:17,120
If I tell anyone about him,
the listener will explode,

31
00:01:17,190 --> 00:01:19,590
and time will reset
to this morning.

32
00:01:19,650 --> 00:01:21,360
It may not happen for a while,

33
00:01:21,420 --> 00:01:24,330
but if we keep letting him
have free rein over our lives,

34
00:01:24,390 --> 00:01:25,630
eventually he’ll kill us.

35
00:01:28,730 --> 00:01:29,760
( Grunts )

36
00:01:29,830 --> 00:01:31,630
♪

37
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:44,510
But luckily for me,
I now know about someone else

38
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:48,220
who has special powers
like Kira, Rohan kishibe!

39
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:50,520
I have to find a way
to talk to him somehow!

40
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,290
I have to get him to help me,

41
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:55,220
or we don’t stand a ghost
of a chance of defeating Kira!

42
00:01:56,620 --> 00:01:57,630
Rohan: Hmm.

43
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:02,130
Hayato: Rohan’s already here.

44
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,730
If I approach him directly,

45
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,500
he’ll get blown to smithereens.

46
00:02:06,570 --> 00:02:09,400
Then i’ll be forced
to relive the same morning.

47
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:11,210
I’ve gotta tell Rohan the info

48
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:13,540
without meeting him
face to face.

49
00:02:13,610 --> 00:02:15,840
It’s time to change fate.

50
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:18,110
( Gasps )

51
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:21,580
What? What? My face!

52
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:23,120
What’s going on?!

53
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:25,420
Hang on! Rohan did this to me

54
00:02:25,490 --> 00:02:26,620
when we met that other morning!

55
00:02:26,690 --> 00:02:28,260
( Man sneezes )

56
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,390
Dammit.

57
00:02:30,690 --> 00:02:32,190
( Women laugh )

58
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:33,700
Hayato: But i’ve
been keeping out of sight

59
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,160
this entire time!

60
00:02:35,230 --> 00:02:37,370
There’s no way
Rohan could have seen me!

61
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:40,800
Kira: Once the wheels of fate
are set in motion,

62
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:43,370
