83
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:12,630
Woman: Come on!
The weather report

84
00:04:12,690 --> 00:04:14,730
never said
anything about rain!

85
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,670
Kira: I’m sure
you would like to believe

86
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:22,570
you shattered
your mother’s favorite teapot

87
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:25,470
of your own free will,
but you’d be wrong.

88
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,740
You simply experienced
a reoccurrence

89
00:04:27,810 --> 00:04:30,480
of the pot breaking
from the previous morning.

90
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:32,710
It’s preordained, son.

91
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:34,850
That’s how fate works,

92
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,520
as you’re about to learn.

93
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:39,550
If Rohan transformed you
into a book the morning before,

94
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:41,760
then a book, you shall be.

95
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:43,760
That is what makes
deadly queen’s

96
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:45,790
bites the dust unstoppable.

97
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:49,600
It reverses time and nullifies
the exposure of my identity...

98
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:53,130
Which means
i’ll have the pleasure

99
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,240
of watching Rohan
explode into obsolescence

100
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:58,210
and still make it
to work on time.

101
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:03,140
Hayato: No,
I can’t let Rohan die!

102
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:06,410
I have to go save him
before it’s too late!

103
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,750
( Gasping )

104
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:10,690
♪

105
00:05:16,690 --> 00:05:18,790
- ( Rohan groans )
- ( Hayato gasps )

106
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:24,830
Kira: Poor Rohan kishibe.

107
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:27,670
- ( Hayato crying )
- Kira: Now watch carefully.

108
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,740
The fool has absolutely no idea

109
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,840
why he’s about to breathe
his last. ( Chuckles )

110
00:05:32,910 --> 00:05:34,510
But i’m sure he’s realized

111
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:37,850
that his life as a manga artist
has come to an end.

112
00:05:37,910 --> 00:05:41,420
( Rohan gasping )

113
00:05:44,890 --> 00:05:47,490
- ( Hayato gasps )
- Rohan: Koichi!

114
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,260
( Hayato sobs )

115
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,690
Reimi: Huh?

116
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,690
( Gasps )

117
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:55,300
♪

118
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,300
( Gasping )

119
00:05:57,370 --> 00:05:59,670
No, not Rohan!

120
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:06,610
Oh, god, why?!

121
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:11,580
( Hayato shuddering )

122
00:06:11,650 --> 00:06:13,720
Kira: Hayato,
your visit with Rohan

123
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:15,820
is now as if it never happened,

124
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:18,650
and the morning will go on
as it always would.

125
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,790
Of course, I could undo
bites the dust right now,

126
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:23,490
which means that rohan’s death

127
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,530
would become
a permanent temporal point,

128
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:28,160
but, for now, I think
i’ll let it do its thing.

129
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:31,230
I suspect a few of his cohorts
will be dropping by shortly.

130
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,530
When they do,

131
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,240
you’re going
to make me a proud papa

132
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,470
by exterminating
the lot of them.

133
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:39,370
You’re my own
personal land mine.

134
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,780
( Laughs ) But chin up.

135
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:44,080
As long as you’re
a good little secret weapon,

136
00:06:44,150 --> 00:06:46,210
bites the dust won’t harm you.

137
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:49,250
So, relax, and do
whatever you schoolboys do.

138
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:51,690
( Chuckles )

139
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,790
Well, daddy’s
off to the station.

140
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,590
No slacking at school now.

141
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:58,690
( Hayato crying )

142
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:01,330
This is only happening,

143
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,670
because he
crossed paths with me.

144
00:07:03,730 --> 00:07:07,200
It’s my fault! He met me
and got murdered for it!

145
00:07:07,270 --> 00:07:08,240
( Gasps )

146
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,310
What now?

147
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:24,050
Isn’t there anything
I can do to stop this monster?

148
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:33,800
Koichi: Pardon me.
Can I ask you a question?

149
00:07:33,860 --> 00:07:36,360
Would you happen
to have the time?

150
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:39,500
My stupid watch seems to be
out of commission.

151
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:41,300
Hello in there. Anyone home?

152
00:07:41,370 --> 00:07:42,300
Hayato: Huh?

153
00:07:45,370 --> 00:07:47,580
Yeah, it’s 8:33.

154
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:50,080
Koichi: You know,
I have this weird feeling

155
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:51,310
i’ve seen you before.

156
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:53,210
Now, where was it?

157
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,220
You wouldn’t happen to know
who I am, would you?

158
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,680
Hayato: No.

159
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:58,790
Koichi: Oh, well. My mistake.

160
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:01,620
I hope I didn’t
weird you out or anything,

161
00:08:01,690 --> 00:08:04,360
but now I know it’s 8:33.
Thanks!

162
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:06,060
( Hayato gasps )

163
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:09,330
Koichi: Mr. Jotaro,
looks like it is after 8:30.

164
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:13,700
How strange. Rohan-sensei knew
we were coming. Where’d he go?

165
00:08:13,770 --> 00:08:15,770
Hayato: These are
Rohan kishibe’s friends!

166
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,470
They planned to meet here!

167
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:19,170
Koichi: He left
the car door wide open...

168
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,340
Hayato: They must have
the same kind of powers as him,

169
00:08:21,410 --> 00:08:22,680
so I bet they all came here

170
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,450
to question me
about yoshikage Kira.

171
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:25,450
Jotaro: Hmm.

172
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:31,290
( Grunts )

173
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:33,250
Hayato: No, no, no, no, no!

174
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,060
If they figure out
i’m hayato kawajiri

175
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:37,390
and start interrogating me
about dad,

176
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,560
it’s all over for them!

177
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,700
( Yelps )

178
00:08:42,830 --> 00:08:45,570
Josuke: Sorry about that, kid.
I was looking for my friends,

179
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,340
and i’m still kinda groggy
from oversleeping.

180
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,470
Okuyasu: I know i’ve seen
this kid’s face before,

181
00:08:49,540 --> 00:08:51,570
but, for the life of me,
I can’t remember where.

182
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,570
( Hayato gasps )

183
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,710
Koichi: Hey, look.
It’s josuke and okuyasu.

184
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:57,780
- Josuke: What’s up, bro?
- Okuyasu: Yo, koichi.

185
00:08:57,850 --> 00:08:59,680
Hope your morning’s
been spiffy, jotaro.

186
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:00,780
Josuke: So we’re
still waiting...

187
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:02,650
Hayato: Th-there
are two more of them.

188
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:05,420
Kira told me that others
would eventually be showing up.

189
00:09:05,490 --> 00:09:07,320
He was talking about them!

190
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:10,360
Josuke: ...Kid’s house
without Rohan helping us out?

191
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:11,690
Uh, sorry.

192
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:14,360
I nearly forgot I was
still hanging on to this.

193
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:16,530
I believe this is yours.

194
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:19,570
Hayato: Oh, thanks a lot.

195
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:22,570
Koichi: You know,
it might be the angle.

196
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,470
Oh, yeah, i’m sure of it.

197
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:27,180
I know i’ve seen
that face before.

198
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,510
I don’t know from where,

199
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:31,180
but he looks too familiar
to be a stranger.

200
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:33,780
Jotaro: Koichi, look
at the name on his backpack.

201
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:37,190
Koichi: Huh? Hayato kawajiri?!

202
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,790
Josuke and okuyasu: What?!

203
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:41,660
Hayato: Crap,
they figured me out!

204
00:09:48,130 --> 00:09:49,230
( Hayato gasping )

205
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,970
Jotaro: Hayato kawajiri.

206
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:53,070
Okuyasu: What the hell
are you doing here?

207
00:09:53,130 --> 00:09:55,270
- Josuke: Was all this planned?
- Koichi: Wait.

208
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:58,040
Could this have something
to do with Rohan-sensei?

209
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:01,110
( Hayato gasps )
What am I supposed to do now?

210
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:04,710
If these guys start questioning
me about my dad, it’s all over.

211
00:10:04,780 --> 00:10:07,020
The bomb will kill
every one of them!

212
00:10:08,650 --> 00:10:11,250
No, please don’t ask me
any questions.

213
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:14,220
If you guys
end up getting killed

214
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:16,290
who’s gonna get rid
of the murderer?

215
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:19,060
If I have to dupe them,
then so be it.

216
00:10:19,130 --> 00:10:22,730
Whatever it takes,
I can’t let them die!

217
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:27,200
Jotaro: I’d like to ask you
about this photo.

218
00:10:27,270 --> 00:10:29,600
To be more precise,

219
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:32,210
I want to know the reason
behind your video recording.

220
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:33,710
Be straight with me.

221
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:34,810
- Why were you--
- ( Hayato wails )

222
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:37,610
Shoot! Nosebleed! Oh, no!

223
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:39,810
I don’t know why my nose
started bleeding out of nowhere,

224
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:41,150
but I have to find a doctor!

225
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:43,150
- Sorry!
- Josuke: Hold it.

226
00:10:43,220 --> 00:10:46,660
You said you got a nosebleed,
huh? Let’s see it.

227
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,860
Come on. Let me see.

228
00:10:50,930 --> 00:10:52,060
( Hayato groans )

229
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:54,860
It’s bad. I need a doctor.

230
00:10:54,930 --> 00:10:58,600
Josuke: Nah, I don’t think
it’s that bad.

231
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:00,170
- Hayato: Huh?
- Josuke: See?

232
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,170
- It’s not even bleeding.
- Hayato: Huh?

233
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:05,970
( Josuke chuckles )

234
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:08,110
Josuke higashikata.
Nice to meet you.

235
00:11:08,180 --> 00:11:11,210
That’s jotaro kujo,
one of my relatives.

236
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:14,050
Derp-face over there
is okuyasu nijimura,

237
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:16,990
and that’s koichi hirose,
the nicest guy I know.

238
00:11:17,050 --> 00:11:19,620
You go to budogaoka elementary,

239
00:11:19,690 --> 00:11:21,990
so you’ve got some time
before class starts.

240
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:23,990
We won’t take up
much of your time.

241
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:26,990
- Now, about this picture...
- ( Hayato gasps )

242
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:30,030
Josuke: If it’s nothing,
we’ll just be on our way.

243
00:11:30,100 --> 00:11:31,600
Hayato: It is something,

244
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:33,970
but I can’t answer
any of your questions!

245
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:36,040
Please don’t ask!

246
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:37,740
Josuke: You see
the man you’re filming?

247
00:11:37,810 --> 00:11:39,670
Would he happen to be your--

248
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:43,040
hayato: I’m begging you!
Don’t say anything else!

249
00:11:43,110 --> 00:11:44,850
( All gasp )

250
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,850
Hayato: Crap. What have I done?

