00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:51,320
Now they’re going to ask
even more questions.

252
00:11:53,090 --> 00:11:54,890
Josuke: What do you mean,
"don’t say anything else"?

253
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,260
Hayato: They’re not gonna stop.

254
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,060
Jotaro: Just what is it
that we shouldn’t say?

255
00:11:58,130 --> 00:11:59,630
Hayato:
There’s nothing I can do!

256
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:01,800
Koichi: Does all of this
have to do with your dad?

257
00:12:01,860 --> 00:12:04,570
Hayato: The bomb’s gonna go off!
It’s gonna kill them all!

258
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:06,130
( Crying )

259
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,970
Koichi: What the hell’s
going on, huh?

260
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:09,600
Josuke: Why can’t
we say anything else?

261
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:10,870
Okuyasu: Yeah. I mean,

262
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:12,310
we haven’t even
asked him anything yet.

263
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:13,980
- Jotaro: Given his reaction...
- ( Hayato muttering )

264
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:16,550
Jotaro: It seems the mere act
of us questioning the kid

265
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:19,080
is what’s sending him
into a panic.

266
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,220
Koichi: That’s it.

267
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:25,590
I have no other choice.

268
00:12:25,650 --> 00:12:28,190
If I die here,
they’ll still be able to live!

269
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:31,790
I’m the bomb, so I have to die!

270
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:33,890
With me out of the picture,

271
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,760
I know these guys
will figure out

272
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:39,100
a way to defeat that devil
and save mom!

273
00:12:39,170 --> 00:12:40,970
- ( Gasps )
- ( Crunch )

274
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,900
Josuke: It shouldn’t
be this difficult.

275
00:12:42,970 --> 00:12:46,040
Let’s just ask him
about kosaku kawajiri already.

276
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:49,110
Jotaro: Hold on, josuke.
Something is up with him.

277
00:12:49,180 --> 00:12:51,080
Boys: Huh?

278
00:12:51,150 --> 00:12:53,880
Jotaro: Hey, what’s wrong?

279
00:12:53,950 --> 00:12:54,980
Hey!

280
00:12:55,050 --> 00:12:56,850
( Hayato gasping )

281
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,820
( All gasp )

282
00:12:58,890 --> 00:13:00,960
Hayato: No, I can’t do it!

283
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:03,290
Something’s keeping me
from slashing my throat!

284
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,890
- Jotaro: Wait! What?!
- Josuke: Isn’t that kira’s?!

285
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:08,200
Okuyasu: Yeah, it is!
That’s a face i’d never forget!

286
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:09,560
Koichi: It’s deadly queen!

287
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:11,570
( Star platinum yells )

288
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,570
Kira: Actually,
you’re looking at deadly queen’s

289
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:19,570
bomb type three, bites the dust.

290
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:21,840
To attack me now
would be futile.

291
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,880
In fact, the only reason
you can see me

292
00:13:23,950 --> 00:13:26,550
is because i’ve already
entered your pupils.

293
00:13:26,610 --> 00:13:27,880
- ( Josuke gasps )
- Kira: It doesn’t matter

294
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:30,550
how many of you
have gathered together.

295
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:32,950
The moment you asked
about my true identity,

296
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:34,320
your fate was sealed!

297
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:36,760
( Trigger clicks )

298
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:40,800
( Hayato screaming )

299
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:51,210
( Screams )

300
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:53,880
Shinobu: Oh, hayato.
I guess you’re already awake.

301
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:56,340
I’m glad you finally decided
to answer me,

302
00:13:56,410 --> 00:13:59,210
but there’s no need to scream
this early in the morning.

303
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:01,080
Breakfast is ready.
Come and get it.

304
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:02,620
( Door closes )

305
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:04,190
( Hayato crying )

306
00:14:08,090 --> 00:14:11,290
I tried,
but I couldn’t stop him.

307
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,230
He got them, too.

308
00:14:13,290 --> 00:14:15,730
It doesn’t matter what I do now.

309
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:17,900
In one hour,
fate will run its course,

310
00:14:17,970 --> 00:14:19,100
and Rohan and his friends

311
00:14:19,170 --> 00:14:21,040
will be wiped
off the face of the earth.

312
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,840
It’s over. It’s all my fault.

313
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:24,970
I can’t even kill myself.

314
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:28,740
If I died, he wouldn’t
be able to use his power,

315
00:14:28,810 --> 00:14:31,910
but bites the dust
is programmed to protect me.

316
00:14:31,980 --> 00:14:34,320
He’s unstoppable!

317
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:37,720
Yoshikage Kira is a monster!

318
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:40,020
Unless he dies
or decides to shut off

319
00:14:40,090 --> 00:14:42,290
bites the dust
at just the right time,

320
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:44,990
those guys are
gonna be blown sky high.

321
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:46,860
He’s made sure of it.

322
00:14:56,070 --> 00:14:57,540
( Sighs )

323
00:14:57,610 --> 00:14:59,110
♪

324
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,680
He either has to die,

325
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:06,980
or shut off bites the dust
at just the right moment.

326
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:11,850
It’s crazy. I never
thought i’d ever be capable

327
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:15,120
of something like killing
a person in cold blood.

328
00:15:15,190 --> 00:15:18,530
I mean, i’m a puny
11-year-old kid.

329
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:21,200
What could I do
against a monster like him?

330
00:15:21,260 --> 00:15:24,570
A-a monster.

331
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:26,830
That’s it! 11 years old or not,

332
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:30,100
there’s one thing I can use
to take him down for good.

333
00:15:31,740 --> 00:15:34,640
Kira called me
his secret weapon earlier.

334
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:36,810
Well, i’ve got my own weapon,

335
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:39,880
and it’s slumbering
in the shadows of the attic.

336
00:15:39,950 --> 00:15:43,890
I’ve never prayed before,
but, if there’s a god out there,

337
00:15:43,950 --> 00:15:46,220
I need you
to come through for me.

338
00:15:46,290 --> 00:15:49,020
Please, god,
help me find the strength

339
00:15:49,090 --> 00:15:51,760
to kill this homicidal maniac.

340
00:15:59,170 --> 00:16:00,700
- ( Gasps )
- ( Feral cat meows )

341
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:02,200
( Hayato gasps )

342
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:04,570
- ( Feral cat growling )
- Hayato: So I was right.

343
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:07,080
The sun makes
this cat plant spring to life.

344
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:08,640
Then it attacks its target

345
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:10,650
by shooting bullets
of compressed air.

346
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:13,250
It’s incredible
it can generate so much power

347
00:16:13,310 --> 00:16:15,250
with such little light. Awesome.

348
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:18,190
I’ll use its killer instinct
to send an air bullet

349
00:16:18,250 --> 00:16:21,020
flying kira’s way
at point-blank range.

350
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:26,960
I have a plan, but when and how
should I execute it?

351
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:31,800
Mom’s here, so I can’t
do it inside or nearby.

352
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,100
Oh, yeah, my hat!

353
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:37,710
When I leave,
he’ll put it on my head.

354
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:40,680
That’ll be my chance.

355
00:16:40,740 --> 00:16:44,550
He’ll come up right behind me,
right into point-blank range.

356
00:16:44,610 --> 00:16:46,150
That’s when i’ll get him!

357
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:48,080
( Anchor coughs )

358
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:51,290
You’re kidding! Why didn’t
you say we were on the air?!

359
00:16:51,350 --> 00:16:53,820
Good morning, all. It’s 7:55...

360
00:16:53,890 --> 00:16:55,090
Hayato: I’m pretty sure dad said

361
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,690
he wanted
another cup of coffee.

362
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:57,730
Shinobu: Hmm?

363
00:16:58,930 --> 00:17:00,930
( Telephone rings )

364
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:05,130
Hayato: Kawajiri residence.

365
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,940
No, wrong number.

366
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:09,600
This isn’t
the sakurai residence.

367
00:17:18,050 --> 00:17:20,280
Shinobu: Sweetie, I have
something special for you.

368
00:17:20,350 --> 00:17:21,980
- Come drink.
- ( Kira grumbles )

369
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:24,590
Shinobu: It’s a piping-hot
cup of fresh coffee.

370
00:17:28,290 --> 00:17:29,820
Kira: Hmm.

371
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:31,860
Oh, what the hell?

372
00:17:31,930 --> 00:17:33,800
It’s such a pleasant morning.

373
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:36,260
I suppose one more cup
before I leave for work

374
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:37,630
wouldn’t hurt anything.

375
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:39,300
Hayato: Everything
is set in stone

376
00:17:39,370 --> 00:17:41,640
under bite the dust’s power,
right?

377
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:44,540
Once something is broken,
it’s destined to break again,

378
00:17:44,610 --> 00:17:47,040
and there’s
not a damn thing I can do.

379
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:49,180
You said it yourself.

380
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:51,150
( Kira gasps )

381
00:17:51,210 --> 00:17:53,150
( Shinobu wails )

382
00:17:53,210 --> 00:17:55,950
Oh, no!
My favorite China tea set!

383
00:17:56,020 --> 00:17:57,490
( Moans )

384
00:17:57,550 --> 00:17:58,920
Hayato: Take that, ass!

385
00:17:58,990 --> 00:18:00,890
All right, mom, see you later!

386
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:03,490
I’m off to school now!
( Chuckles )

387
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:04,930
- ( Kiss )
- ( Shinobu gasps )

388
00:18:04,990 --> 00:18:07,260
Hayato: There’s nothing
to worry about.

389
00:18:07,330 --> 00:18:10,700
I’ll never let anyone
hurt you, mom. Trust me.

390
00:18:15,340 --> 00:18:17,240
( Kira growls )

391
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,610
Shinobu: Where did
that come from?

392
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,910
He’s always so aloof.

393
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:28,550
I never know
what’s going on in his head,

394
00:18:28,620 --> 00:18:31,250
but then we have
mornings like this one,

395
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:33,220
and I can’t help but love him.

396
00:18:33,290 --> 00:18:36,990
Let me. I’ll have this
cleaned up in a jiff.

397
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:39,230
No use crying
over spilled coffee,

398
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:41,930
but I hope it
didn’t burn you too badly.

399
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,870
Kira: It’s fine. Don’t worry.

400
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:46,870
♪

401
00:18:51,270 --> 00:18:53,140
Hayato: He’s still not here.

402
00:18:53,210 --> 00:18:54,940
( Women laugh )

403
00:18:55,010 --> 00:18:56,710
Hayato: Where is he?

404
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:59,110
Why hasn’t he shown up yet?

405
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:00,480
Huh?

406
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:01,850
What’s going on?

407
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,680
He was already here last time!

408
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,120
What’s the holdup?

409
00:19:05,190 --> 00:19:06,590
Woman: Come on!
The weather report

410
00:19:06,650 --> 00:19:07,920
never said anything about rain.

411
00:19:07,990 --> 00:19:10,020
Hayato: No. It’s already
beginning to rain!

412
00:19:10,090 --> 00:19:12,960
I wonder if I
accidently changed destiny

413
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:15,230
by leaving the house
before he did.

414
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:17,200
No, that’s impossible.

415
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:20,270
If he’s gonna try and sneak up
to put the hat on my head,

416
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:23,040
there’s no question he’ll
try approaching me from behind.

417
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:27,680
Time is running out!
Lightning struck the Pepsi sign!

418
00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:31,150
I’ve gotta calm down.
I’ve still got two minutes,

419
00:19:31,210 --> 00:19:32,850
and I have more than two minutes

420
00:19:32,910 --> 00:19:35,950
before Rohan kishibe
spontaneously explodes.

421
00:19:36,020 --> 00:19:37,290
I just have to believe--

422
00:19:37,350 --> 00:19:39,890
( gasping )

423
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:44,630
He’s hiding
in the shadow of the tree.

424
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:47,660
He’s been here all along.
How could I have missed that?

425
00:19:47,730 --> 00:19:50,300
Kira: Under
any other circumstance,

426
00:19:50,370 --> 00:19:52,300
i’d say this morning
was pleasant,

427
00:19:52,370 --> 00:19:54,070
but hayato wasn’t himself.

428
00:19:54,140 --> 00:19:55,270
Why, though?

429
00:19:55,340 --> 00:19:57,710
I’m getting
a very strange feeling.

430
00:19:57,770 --> 00:20:01,080
It feels like we’ve relived
this morning several times now,

431
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:02,280
maybe three--

432
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:04,280
no, wait. At least four times.

433
00:20:04,350 --> 00:20:07,280
Hayato: Oh, no. Does he sense
that something’s not right?

434
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,880
It doesn’t matter.
There’s no time!

435
00:20:09,950 --> 00:20:13,660
I have no other choice
but to blast him from here!

436
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:15,820
- ( Feral cat growling )
- ( Hayato gasps )

437
00:20:15,890 --> 00:20:18,330
Could he have figured out
that i’m gonna use the cat plant

438
00:20:18,390 --> 00:20:19,960
as a weapon to take him out?

439
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:22,030
Is that why he’s deciding
to keep his distance?

440
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:25,170
No way. If he knew,
he wouldn’t be that close.

441
00:20:25,230 --> 00:20:28,040
Okay, i’m only gonna get
one shot to finish him off,

442
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:29,800
so I have to make it count.

443
00:20:29,870 --> 00:20:33,710
If I miss, Rohan will explode,
his friends will be obliterated,

444
00:20:33,780 --> 00:20:36,240
and that murderer
will deactivate bites the dust,

445
00:20:36,310 --> 00:20:38,350
making
the whole thing permanent!

446
00:20:38,410 --> 00:20:41,080
If that happens,
he ends up the Victor.

447
00:20:41,150 --> 00:20:42,780
It’s now or never.

448
00:20:42,850 --> 00:20:45,150
Just take
one more step to the left!

449
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:47,890
Hurry up, and step out from
the shadow of that shitty tree

450
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:50,090
so I can blow you
to kingdom come!

451
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:53,800
( Gasps ) What the hell?!

452
00:20:53,860 --> 00:20:55,700
He hid himself even more!

453
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:57,930
Kira: The look
in hayato’s eyes this morning

454
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:01,040
radiated a tenacity
i’ve never seen in him.

455
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:03,240
It was almost
the exact same look those louts,

456
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:05,840
koichi hirose and josuke,
gave off.

457
00:21:05,910 --> 00:21:07,810
I don’t know what it is,

458
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:10,910
but something’s telling me
I need to watch his every move.

459
00:21:10,980 --> 00:21:14,650
Then again, as it stands,
hayato’s completely helpless.

460
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:16,320
Hayato: Shit, i’m screwed!

461
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:18,320
A few seconds past 8:29,

462
00:21:18,390 --> 00:21:21,290
and the bomb will start
ripping Rohan kishibe apart!

463
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:22,620
Kira: Hmm.

464
00:21:24,690 --> 00:21:26,660
What is this?

465
00:21:26,730 --> 00:21:28,260
The brat is panic-stricken.

466
00:21:28,330 --> 00:21:29,730
He’s like a desperate rat,

467
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:31,830
toiling and drowning
in a cesspool of filth.

468
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:35,240
I guess I was
imagining his tenacity.

469
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:37,740
Those are the eyes of defeat.

470
00:21:37,810 --> 00:21:40,140
( Hayato gasps ) He came out!

471
00:21:41,380 --> 00:21:43,140
Kira: You left home
without your hat,

472
00:21:43,210 --> 00:21:45,010
so I thought
i’d bring it to you.

473
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:49,950
Hayato: If you’re listening
up there, thank you, god.

474
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:52,250
Thanks for working your magic
and making that murderer

475
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:54,720
leave the safety
of that tree’s shadow.

476
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:57,030
I’m ready to do this!

477
00:21:57,090 --> 00:21:59,590
Now die, yoshikage Kira!

478
00:21:59,660 --> 00:22:01,800
( Feral cat growls )

479
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,830
( Kira gasps )

480
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:07,740
What the--

481
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:09,240
( gags )

482
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:10,840
( Hayato gasps ) I did it!

483
00:22:10,910 --> 00:22:13,040
♪

484
00:22:13,110 --> 00:22:16,840
A clean shot. I did it!

485
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:19,250
Rohan: He still
hasn’t shown up yet.

486
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:21,820
Perhaps he took
a different route to school

487
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,120
and I missed him.

488
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:24,190
( Hayato growls )

489
00:22:26,890 --> 00:22:29,590
Prepare to die, murderer!

490
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:30,660
Huh?

491
00:22:35,060 --> 00:22:36,900
What the hell?!

492
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:39,130
Kira: You know, as of late...

493
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,940
Hayato: No way!

494
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:43,710
Kira: My nails have shown
unprecedented growth,

495
00:22:43,770 --> 00:22:45,570
which got me thinking about

496
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:49,140
how lately my life has been
devoid of all that is good.

497
00:22:49,210 --> 00:22:52,310
But the contents of this pocket
confirm my feeling

498
00:22:52,380 --> 00:22:56,150
that a guardian angel
has returned to watch over me.

